## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e2ec0-106">這個類別會提供.NET framework 中 installUtil 標準安裝程式的介面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e2ec0-106">This class provides an interface for the standard installUtil installer in the .NET framework.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e2ec0-107">包含 Automation 類別之任何組件應該包括來自此類型衍生的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e2ec0-107">Any assembly that contains Automation classes should include a class that is derived from this type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e2ec0-108">這將提供產生的 automation 物件的結構描述、 將它安裝到 WMI 中，並建立必要的提供者登錄程式碼的程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e2ec0-108">This will provide code that generates the schema of the automation objects, installs it into WMI, and creates the necessary provider registration code.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e2ec0-109">下列範例示範如何自<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.DefaultManagementInstaller>類別來安裝 WMI 提供者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e2ec0-109">The following example shows how to derive a class from the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.DefaultManagementInstaller> class to install a WMI provider.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// This is the installer class that installs an instrumented assembly.  
// To use the default project installer, simply derive a class from  
// DefaultManagementInstaller.  No methods need to be overridden.  
[System.ComponentModel.RunInstaller(true)]  
public class TheInstaller : DefaultManagementInstaller  
{ }  
```
